						{ 
							"I hope Gio's doing alright. It's been a few days since we talked last. "
							--
							"\s[1]He's been quite well, I think...\s[0]\n Busy, but well."
							"\s[3]I heard from a mutual friend of ours that he's not doing so hot... \s[1]perhaps I will send him a small care package. Do you think he would enjoy a little delivery of tea blends and biscuits?.."
						}
						"I hear Gio's well, at least. I've been meaning to visit him, but... well, you know. \s[1]Busy..."
