			//gio
			"\0\s[1]I try not to talk anyone's ear off about my Guardian friends, but it really is hard not to mention Gio more often... he always beckons me not to compare, tells me I have my own long list of duties, but he truly does impress me. He deals a lot more with people than I ever do; of course, his students can take some of the workload, just like mine... but he still has to listen to the confessions of hundreds of people every week. \s[0]I simply couldn't do it! I mean... I'd just want to gossip with them all. I don't know how he makes them feel cleansed of their wrongdoings and all that... \s[1]and what of the people who really are awful?! Does he still 'forgive' them? What of murderers and the like?.. It's all such a thrill to think about, \s[0]but he never tells me, of course. He knows I blab too much!.. \s[1]Perhaps he'll spill his methods someday."
			
			//claris
			"\0\s[0]Claris has been hard at work on repairing the Shrine of Clubs... \w9again. \s[1]I feel so bad for her, she has to put up with earthquakes so often...\n It leads me to count my blessings, here at this temple. I am very thankful for the lack of disasters here...\n\n \s[0]The energy surrounding the shrines are often as calm as the Ace they were built after. Nore of Clubs was... \s[3]not very calm, to put it lightly. \s[0]A hectic energy surrounds the Lamnthine temple, especially in the Selyrtime..."
			
